Interface SignalDatabase

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Subinterfaces:
LoadableSignalDatabase
All Known Implementing Classes:
LoadableSignalDatabaseImpl, SignalDatabaseImpl, SimulationCompressedUWI, SimulationHSpiceAscii, SimulationHSpiceCSDF, SimulationNonCompressedUWI, SimulationPsfAscii, SimulationPsfAsciiDC
public interface SignalDatabase
extends java.io.Serializable, IndexedSignals, NamesIndex

SimulationOutput stores raw simulation output data, these are waveforms (signals) which can be accessed by their name or by their index. note: is it a good idea to make the interface serializable ? e.g. will all implementations be serializable

Author:
scoseman
